*** Settings ***
Documentation    Textarea validations: multiline content is preserved through a
...              fill-then-read round-trip, verifying that the browser / app does
...              not collapse newlines. All project-agnostic.
...              Generated by scripts/new_keyword.py for form_validation/text_area.resource.
Library          Browser
Resource         _helpers.resource


*** Keywords ***
Validate Text Area Multiline Preserved
    [Documentation]    Builds a 3-line string (``Line 1${newline}Line 2${newline}Line 3``)
    ...                using Robot Framework's built-in ``${\n}`` variable,
    ...                fills the textarea using ``Fill Text`` (which preserves
    ...                newlines), triggers validation, then reads the element's
    ...                ``value`` property and asserts it equals the original
    ...                multi-line input exactly.
    ...
    ...                Behavior:
    ...                1. Constructs a 3-line input string with newline separators.
    ...                2. Fills the textarea with the multi-line content.
    ...                3. Triggers validation via ``${trigger}``.
    ...                4. Reads the textarea's ``value`` property.
    ...                5. Asserts the read-back value equals the input verbatim
    ...                   (no whitespace mangling, newlines preserved).
    ...
    ...                Arguments:
    ...                - ``field_locator``   — Playwright selector of the textarea.
    ...                - ``trigger``         — ``blur`` (default) or ``submit``.
    ...                - ``submit_locator``  — required when ``trigger=submit``.
    [Arguments]    ${field_locator}
    ...            ${trigger}=blur    ${submit_locator}=${EMPTY}
    ${multiline}=    Catenate    SEPARATOR=${\n}    Line 1    Line 2    Line 3
    Fill Text    ${field_locator}    ${multiline}
    Trigger Field Validation    ${field_locator}    ${trigger}    ${submit_locator}
    ${actual}=    Get Property    ${field_locator}    value
    Should Be Equal    ${actual}    ${multiline}
    ...    msg=Textarea multiline round-trip failed: expected newlines preserved, got: ${actual}
